author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! Video games in recent years have been losing official support and have been unfortunately positioned to not be preserved as time goes on. An alarming report from the volunteers at "Stop Killing Games" has pointed out hundreds of popular games at risk of being completely gone forever. Let's try and change things. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Video Games Are Dying Rapidly...
